Oakland.Havenscourt, Oakland, California:
Havenscourt is a neighborhood of Oakland in Alameda County, California.


== Schools ==
Middle schools located in the Havenscourt neighborhood include the Coliseum College Prep Academy at Havenscourt, and the Roots International Academy at Havenscourt, which were created in 2006 from the breakup of Havenscourt Middle School.
